Version 2.0.3
-------------

* Add serialize method

Version 2.0.2
-------------

* Raise exception in both HIPCHAT_URL and HIPCHAT_DOMAIN are set.
  - Currently there is a bug where nothing happens when both are set

Version 2.0.1
-------------

* Make it backwards compatible
  - If HIPCHAT_URL exists, v1 api will be used, otherwise v2 will be used

Version 2.0.0
-------------

* Switch to using hipchat API v2
  - Now uses the HIPCHAT_DOMAIN for custom hipchat deployments
  - Will extract the domain from HIPCHAT_URL if it exists (for backwards compatibility)
